data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Are you looking for a new home in Winter Haven, FL? We have the perfect property for you! Located at 1001 34th Street NW in Winter Haven, this home is currently for sale. This charming home has 2 Bedrooms with a BONUS room! The roof is newer! This is the ideal place to call home. Situated in the desirable area of Winter Haven, this home offers convenient access to schools, parks, shopping centers, and restaurants, ensuring you'll have everything you need just minutes away. The property also boasts a lovely backyard where you can relax and unwind after a long day. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Call our real estate agent today and start making new memories in your dream.
